OLED Display (SSD1306)	SDA = GPIO 21, SCL = GPIO 22	

Joystick X-axis (VRx)	GPIO 34	Analog input

Joystick Y-axis (VRy)	GPIO 35	Analog input

Joystick Button (SW)	GPIO 32	Digital input 

Back Button	GPIO 33	Digital input 

Ultrasonic Sensor TRIG	GPIO 25	Digital output → TRIG pin

Ultrasonic Sensor ECHO	GPIO 26	Digital input ← ECHO pin

Buzzer	GPIO 27	Digital output

Thermistor (10k NTC)	Divider to GPIO 36 (ADC1_CH0)	One leg → 3.3V; other leg → junction with 10k resistor and also to GPIO36


3.3V
    │  [one leg]
    │
 [10kΩ Thermistor]
    │  [other leg]
    ├───► GPIO36 
    │
 [10kΩ Resistor]
    │
   GND


Fixed Resistor (10k)	Divider for Thermistor	One leg → GND, other leg → junction with Thermistor & GPIO36


LDR (Light Sensor)	Divider to GPIO 39 (ADC1_CH3)	One leg → 3.3V; other leg → junction with 10k resistor and also to GPIO39

3.3V
    │  [one leg]
    │
 [  LDR  ]
    │  [other leg]
    ├───► GPIO36 
    │
 [10kΩ Resistor]
    │
   GND


Fixed Resistor (10k)	Divider for LDR	One leg → GND, other leg → junction with LDR & GPIO39

nRF24L01+ CE	GPIO 5	CE pin

nRF24L01+ CSN	GPIO 4	CSN pin

nRF24L01+ MOSI	GPIO 23	SPI MOSI

nRF24L01+ MISO	GPIO 19	SPI MISO

nRF24L01+ SCK	GPIO 18	SPI Clock

nRF24L01+ VCC	3.3V	⚡ (Add 10µF capacitor between VCC & GND for stability)

nRF24L01+ GND	GND	Ground



